Title: KitchenAid® Fruit & Vegetable Strainer Parts
Description: Quickly and easily prepare fresh apple or tomato sauce, baby food, freezer jams, and chutneys when you attach the fruit and vegetable strainer parts to your food grinder attachment.

Description: Quickly and easily extract juice from the smallest lime to the largest grapefruit. A special strainer helps trap pulp.

Title: KitchenAid® Flat Beater

Title: KitchenAid® Dough Hook
Description: The dough hook mixes and kneads yeast dough, saving both time and effort of hand-kneading. Fits all tilt-head Stand Mixers.
